# Versioner GitHub Action - Development Guide

## Project Type
TypeScript GitHub Action using @vercel/ncc for bundling

## Documentation Strategy

**Single Source of Project/Development plan:** `TODO.md`
- This is the canonical plan tracking all phases and tasks
- Update it as you complete tasks (mark ✅, add notes, issues)
- Don't create new status files or session summaries

**Keep Documentation DRY:**
- Consolidate related information into existing docs whenever possible
- Avoid duplicate content across files
- Delete outdated or redundant docs

